  "raw_html": "<button type='button' role='link' class='btn btn-link p-0 text-start' id='link_5' aria-label=\" INOX Air Products Limited now known as INOX Air Products Private Limited and Another versus The State of Andhra Pradesh pdf\"  class='noToken' href='#' onclick=javascript:open_pdf('5','2025','2025_1_1235_1255','2025INSC128'); ><font size='4'> <strong>INOX AIR PRODUCTS LIMITED NOW KNOWN AS INOX AIR PRODUCTS PRIVATE LIMITED AND ANOTHER<span class='fst-italic'> versus </span>THE STATE OF ANDHRA PRADESH </strong>- <span class='escrText'>[2025] 1 S.C.R. 1235</span><span class='ncDisplay'>2025 INSC 128</span><input type='hidden' id='cnr' value=ESCR010002572025></button></font><br><strong>Coram : BHUSHAN RAMKRISHNA GAVAI<sup style=\"color: #268e97;font-size: 22px;top: 0;\" class=\"tooltip-sup\" data-tooltip=\"Author\">*</sup>, AUGUSTINE GEORGE MASIH</strong><br> Issue for Consideration Whether selling of Nitrous Oxide I.P. by the appellant no. 1 company to the unlicensed accused No.3 firm which does not possess license under Form 20B of the Drugs and Cosmetics Act, 1940, was in contravention r.65(5)(1)(b) of the Rules, punishable u/s.27(d) of the said Act. Headnotes&dagger; Drugs and Cosmetics Act, 1940 &ndash; ss.3(f), 18(a)(vi), 27(d) &ndash; Drugs and Cosmetics Rules, 1945 &ndash; rr.65(5)(1)(b), 70, Form 20B, 25, 26 &ndash; Manufacture and sale of drugs &ndash; Condition of<br><strong class='caseDetailsTD' ><span style='color:#212F3D' > Decision Date :</span><font color='green'> 30-01-2025</font><span style='color:#212F3D' > | Case No :</span><font color='green'> CRIMINAL APPEAL No. 486/2025</font><span style='color:#212F3D' > | Disposal Nature :</span><font color='green'> Appeal(s) allowed</font>   <span style='color:#212F3D' > |  Bench :</span><font color='green'> 2 Judges</font></strong><div class='row my-1 mt-2 border bg-light'><div class='col-auto'><a href='#' class='btn btn-outline-secondary btn-sm my-1' onclick=open_splitview('5','2025','2025_1_1235_125